"{\"uid\": \"gbnews.com-news-world-migrant-crisis-french-patrols-paris-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"WATCH NOW: GB News cover migrants crossing hitting a record high GB NEWS ByMark White Published: 25/04/2024 Updated: 25/04/2024 The French capital will host the major sporting event from July 26 to August 11 Vital migrant patrols along the northern French coast could be \\\"severely impacted\\\" by the need to divert policing resources to cover the Paris Olympics, French policing unions and local officials have claimed.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 423, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 66, \"end\": 73, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GB_News\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"GB NEWS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GB_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/GB_News\"}, {\"begin\": 82, \"end\": 87, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\", \"score\": 0.9985489842683284, \"rank\": 0.0013922864271403996, \"text\": \"White\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/White_people\"}, {\"begin\": 137, \"end\": 143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5417147916687172, \"rank\": 0.5207724254327039, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 255, \"end\": 261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5417147916687172, \"rank\": 0.5207724254327039, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 367, \"end\": 373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5417147916687172, \"rank\": 0.5207724254327039, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"GB News\", \"from\": 11, \"to\": 18}, {\"ngram\": \"migrants crossing\", \"from\": 25, \"to\": 42}, {\"ngram\": \"the major sporting event\", \"from\": 157, \"to\": 181}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 191}, {\"ngram\": \"August 11 Vital migrant patrols\", \"from\": 198, \"to\": 229}, {\"ngram\": \"the need\", \"from\": 294, \"to\": 302}, {\"ngram\": \"policing resources\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 331}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 359}, {\"ngram\": \"local officials\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Police officers from across France are being mobilised to take up duties around the French capital for the major sporting event, from July 26 to August 11.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 580, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 453, \"end\": 459, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_France\", \"score\": 0.9642353395255412, \"rank\": 0.026899583553292708, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Battle_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 509, \"end\": 515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5417147916687172, \"rank\": 0.5207724254327039, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Police officers\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 440}, {\"ngram\": \"duties\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"the major sporting event\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 552}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 563}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics will be a huge logistical and security challenge for the French Government, coming against the backdrop of a heightened terror threat across Europe.Any move to redeploy police away from northern French beaches would come right in the middle of what is normally the busiest period for attempted migrant crossings, the height of summer.French migrants patrols could be 'severely impacted' by need to police Paris Olympics|GETTYThere are currently around 800 police and gendarmes, as well as 400 reservists providing round the clock patrols on a stretch of coastline spanning almost 100 miles.Fr\\u00e9d\\u00e9ric Okonek, a shop steward for the Unite-SGP policing union said: \\\"There are five companies of CRS (French National Police) about 350 personnel, normally dedicated to the fight against illegal immigration who will not be available this summer because they are being requisitioned for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 1487, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 652, \"end\": 669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_France\", \"score\": 0.8961017844713974, \"rank\": 0.1088374734313514, \"text\": \"French Government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 790, \"end\": 796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5417147916687172, \"rank\": 0.5207724254327039, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1000, \"end\": 1014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1194, \"end\": 1200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Okonek\", \"score\": 0.9999999993042366, \"rank\": 6.957193328663368e-10, \"text\": \"Okonek\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Okonek\", \"dbpedia\"