Manston migrant processing centre in Kent.The NCA said a 19-year-old from Sudan, who was initially arrested on Tuesday evening, has been released without charge and will be dealt with instead by immigration authorities.Two other men, both 22, from Sudan and South Sudan, continue to be held in custody and are being questioned on suspicion of facilitating illegal entry to the UK and illegally entering the UK themselves.\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 4965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3745, \"end\": 3751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5417147916687172, \"rank\": 0.5207724254327039, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 3815, \"end\": 3820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.4685420598559923e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 4047, \"end\": 4055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wimereux\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wimereux\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wimereux\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wimereux\"}, {\"begin\": 4381, \"end\": 4402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Crime_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"National Crime Agency\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Crime_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Crime_Agency\"}, {\"begin\": 4507, \"end\": 4512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\", \"score\": 0.9999999074821105, \"rank\": 9.251346756685086e-08, \"text\": \"Sudan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sudan\"}, {\"begin\": 4544, \"end\": 4551, \"title\": \"ht